These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, malaysian, spanish, colombian, indian
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, lily, zinnia, tulip
1. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is in the middle##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
4. the spanish is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the egyptian is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growslily##2
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Nationality          | malaysian | egyptian | indian | colombian | spanish |
| Flower   | lily  | tulip      | zinnia   | dahlia     | balloon-flower    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, folk, salsa
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, bellflower, tulip, poppy, zinnia
1. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the person who growssunflower is between the fan of electronic and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
7. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | folk       | salsa    | ambient | blues   |
| Flower      | bellflower | sunflower | poppy | zinnia      | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, 7up, sprite, lemonade
5 different games are played: poker, chess, domino, backgammon, snooker
1. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Beverage         | tea | 7up | cola | sprite    | lemonade |
| Game   | backgammon     | poker        | domino      | chess | snooker      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian, egyptian, polish
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, azure, amber, blood-red, orange
1. the nigerian is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
4. the polish is the person who likes azure##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the canadian is between the person who likes amber and the polish##2
7. the person who likes orange is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Nationality         | argentine      | egyptian | nigerian | canadian   | polish  |
| Color   | blood-red | orange    | amber        | mauve | azure |

