.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, april, november, august, september
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, freelancer, pilot, electrician, software-developer
1. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the software-developer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the electrician##1
7. the freelancer is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Birthday      | september      | april | july   | august  | november  |
| Job   | pilot | electrician | project-manager | freelancer | software-developer |

