.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, mauve, blue, ivory, chestnut
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, disco, hip-hop, blues, house
1. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
2. the fan of disco is between the fan of house and the person who likes blue##2
3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is the person who likes blue##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
7. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Color   | mauve        | light-blue                | ivory  | blue  | chestnut            |
| Music-Genre        | indie | house | disco | hip-hop | blues |

