.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, lettuce, tomato, nectarine, orange
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, november, may, december, february
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
3. the person eating lettuce is in the middle##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Food   | orange       | tomato   | lettuce    | nectarine    | strawberry |
| Birthday        | may | july | november | february | december     |

