.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, bridge, mah-jongg, poker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: electronic, pop, gospel, house, classical
1. the fan of gospel is the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the fan of house and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Game      | bridge  | billiard       | monopoly      | mah-jongg  | poker   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | house | pop | gospel |

