.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There 5 different types of food: lime, pumpkin, corn, radish, mango
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, collecting, baking, fishing, photography
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
2. the person eating radish is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person eating corn is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating lime##2
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating corn##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Food   | mango | pumpkin | corn     | lime | radish |
| Hobby           | collecting | drawing     | baking | photography    | fishing      |

