.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-10::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, light-blue, red, yellow, pink
City: miami, liverpool, rome, boston, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes red##1
7. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Color     | pink | red | yellow | fuchsia | light-blue |
| City   | rome | berlin | boston    | liverpool    | miami  |

