.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, red, turquise, blood-red, pink
The people have 5 different jobs:  librarian, designer, dressmaker, lawyer, architect
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the designer##3
3. the person who likes black is between the dressmaker and the designer##2
4. the architect is on the right of the dressmaker##1
5. the architect is the person who likes turquise##1
6. the architect is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Color    | red    | pink  | black      | blood-red     | turquise |
| Job   | librarian | designer | lawyer | dressmaker | architect |

