.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, american, colombian, french, australian
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, musical, fantasy, horror
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the chinese##1
3. the person watching horror movies is in the middle##1
4. the american is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching horror movies and the american##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
8. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality        | french | australian | chinese  | colombian | american     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | musical     | horror | epic      | fantasy |

