.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, software-developer, pilotcher, scientist, pilot
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, february, june, november, january
1. the scientist is in an even position##4
2. the pilot is on the left or right of the pilotcher##3
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
4. the scientist is on the right of the software-developer##1
5. the pilotcher is in an even position##4
6. the software-developer is between the person who's birthday is in september and the pilotcher##2
7. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Job      | pilot       | pilotcher | software-developer | scientist   | analyst   |
| Birthday   | november | february | january  | september | june |

