.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, backgammon, poker, go
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, metal, ambient, reggae, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
7. the fan of reggae is between the fan of metal and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game    | go   | poker  | monopoly     | mah-jongg | backgammon |
| Music-Genre   | punk | ambient | folk | reggae | metal      |

