.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
City: new-york, boston, london, rome, berlin
5 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, fish, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
6. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
7. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
8. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| City   | boston  | london    | rome | new-york   | berlin |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla | rabbit    | cat | fish |

