.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-16::.
City: london, marseilles, miami, venice, edinburgh
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, aristoff, swisher, alhambra, pall-mall
1. the person traveling to venice is the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| City           | london | edinburgh | miami | venice | marseilles   |
| Cigar   | aristoff       | swisher            | ritmeester    | alhambra     | pall-mall |

