.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, fonseca, blend, ritmeester
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, golf, handball, parkour
1. the blend-smoker is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
4. the ritmeester-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's sport is basketball##2
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left or far right##3
8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Cigar   | siglo | blend | fonseca     | ritmeester     | tiparillo |
| Sport     | handball   | rugby   | basketball | golf | parkour  |

