.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, british, argentine, italian, egyptian
There 5 different types of food: broccoli, blueberry, nectarine, pear, garlic
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
5. the british is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
6. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
8. the egyptian is on the left of the argentine##1
9. the argentine is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | british | egyptian     | argentine | italian |
| Food     | pear       | blueberry   | nectarine | broccoli   | garlic        |

