.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, chaman, dunhill, siglo, game
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, designer, nurse, librarian
1. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the designer is the designer##1
3. the nurse is on the far left##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
5. the game-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the librarian##2
6. the scientist is between the siglo-smoker and the librarian##2
7. the nurse is in an odd position##4
8. the librarian is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Cigar         | siglo | dunhill | chaman | game | ritmeester     |
| Job   | nurse    | scientist   | librarian       | designer | journalist |

