.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
5 different games are played: bridge, go, whist, billiard, monopoly
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, 7up, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing bridge##1
7. the person playing go is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Game   | bridge | whist      | billiard | monopoly     | go      |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | cola | hot-chocolate | sprite | 7up |

 